msgstr "Though they’re happy there, passages of the teaching don’t come back to them. "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.6"
msgid "api ca kho bhikkhu iddhimā cetovasippatto devaparisāyaṃ dhammaṃ deseti. "
msgstr "However, a mendicant with psychic powers, who has achieved mastery of the mind, teaches Dhamma to the assembly of gods. "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.7"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "They think: "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.8"
msgid "‘ayaṃ vā so dhammavinayo, yatthāhaṃ pubbe brahmacariyaṃ acarin’ti. "
msgstr "‘I used to live the spiritual life in this same teaching and training.’ "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.9"
