msgstr "Memory comes up slowly, "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.10"
msgid "atha so satto khippameva visesagāmī hoti. "
msgstr "but then that being quickly reaches distinction. "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.11"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso kusalo bherisaddassa. "
msgstr "Suppose a person was skilled in the sound of drums. "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.12"
msgid "So addhānamaggappaṭipanno bherisaddaṃ suṇeyya. "
msgstr "While traveling along a road they hear the sound of drums. "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.13"
