msgstr "that was the sound of drums or not. "

msgctxt "an4.191:2.15"
msgid "Atha kho bherisaddotveva niṭṭhaṃ gaccheyya. "
msgstr "They’d just conclude, ‘That’s the sound of drums.’ "

