msgid "‘sarasi tvaṃ, mārisa, sarasi tvaṃ, mārisa, yattha mayaṃ pubbe brahmacariyaṃ acarimhā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Do you remember, good sir? Do you remember where we used to live the spiritual life?’ "

